{"tid":1550913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[求翻譯] 大家一齊喺Twitter表揚大埔護女食棍男","createTime":"2019-09-07T18:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T04:40:27.000Z","uid":148778,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4fcc85061694ed8733e1c0f15a77a90725588da5","tid":1550913,"uid":148778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:37:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/7wr1uoot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2F7wr1uoot&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=92c0df6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/7wr1uoot</a><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊喺Twitter洗板，要俾世界睇到我哋要繼續五大訴求，成立獨立調查委員會就係為咗防止同追究啲咁嘅罪案<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下求翻譯：<br />\n第一段：<br />\n即使我們被囚禁於暴政和法律之下，你仍然可以選擇用身軀和生命去展示你的紳士風度<br />\n<br />\n第二段：<br />\n我們要繼續五大訴求，成立獨立調查委員會就是為了防止和追究這些罪案<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/7wr1uoot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2F7wr1uoot&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=92c0df6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/7wr1uoot</a>(同上)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片段來源post:<br />\n「連登英雄」英勇男為保護兩女，硬食黑警亂棍！（有片）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550730</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303fd2921ed6036c158efe601e46bfc583fc1d12","tid":1550913,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:37:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffe4afba7e93f277ede1e9e5527a11b6de42e3be","tid":1550913,"uid":148778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:39:01.000Z","msg":"求翻譯，如有手足幫手翻譯，請將譯文回覆本留言<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb454601948cb3488ed00a150459666e28e9ba4f","tid":1550913,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:39:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a353acfac7b5374b580a84b774d96c3e6ffbc93","tid":1550913,"uid":148778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:39:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60bd73640acbfd26ccddfadef526d3732e8132eb","tid":1550913,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:40:20.000Z","msg":"[置頂]20190908邊個衝美領就係鬼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550882</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c900b4275df8e3846f588c7f7ab9b09c04f4de21","tid":155